      "title": "Namal\u2019s advice to RW on what to do next",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "MP Namal Rajapakasa said that he believes President Ranil Wickremesinghe should create a stable government with the 134 MPs who voted in favour of him and not those who opposed him.",
        "\u201cThe President should not embrace all the 225 MPs now. What he should instead do is create a stable government with the 134 MPs who voted for him and appoint ministers and state ministers among them. Then we can move forward,\u201d Namal said."
      ],
